CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence standing behind table with woman, and four other men, including Mal Goode on right, in Centre Avenue Y.M.C.A. gymnasium with sign under basketball hoop inscribed "Centre Avenue Branch Y.M.C.A. 1956 Annual Membership Enrollment, William 'Archie' Arvin General Chairman, William W. Goode Co-Chairman, Join your Y now!"
